le="color:#3A95FF">callback</span>    </dt>    <dd>     <p class="para">      See      <a href="https://php.net/manual/zh/ev.watcher-callbacks.php" class="link">Watcher callbacks</a>.     </p>    </dd>          <dt>     <span class="parameter" style="color:#3A95FF">data</span>    </dt>    <dd>     <p class="para">      Custom data associated with the watcher.     </p>    </dd>          <dt>     <span class="parameter" style="color:#3A95FF">priority</span>    </dt>    <dd>     <p class="para">      <a href="https://php.net/manual/zh/class.ev.php#ev.constants.watcher-pri" class="link">Watcher priority</a>     </p>    </dd>     </dl> </div> <div class="refsect1 returnvalues" id="refsect1-evcheck.createstopped-returnvalues">  <h3 class="title">返回值</h3>  <p class="para">   Returns EvCheck object on success.  </p> </div> <div class="refsect1 seealso" id="refsect1-evcheck.createstopped-seealso">  <h3 class="title">参见</h3>  <ul class="simplelist">   <li>    <span class="classname"><a href="https://php.net/manual/zh/class.evprepare.php" class="classname">EvPrepare</a></span>   </li>  </ul> </div></div>
    *
