er again every repeat seconds later, until stopped manually.     </p>    </dd>     </dl> </div> <div class="refsect1 returnvalues" id="refsect1-evtimer.set-returnvalues">  <h3 class="title">返回值</h3>  <p class="para">   没有返回值。  </p> </div></div>
